{"tid":2119582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約移民律師：香港現在真的沒有希望","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T07:46:37.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdcfb36a5f70108d5dbe3bc0ffa5ad4a4254c820","tid":2119582,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200722/K4LJAJ6UOPQNXPACE3XW7FTGUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200722%2FK4LJAJ6UOPQNXPACE3XW7FTGUI%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=76d9f47e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200722%2FK4LJAJ6UOPQNXPACE3XW7FTGUI%2F&h=23d4cb4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200722/K4LJAJ6UOPQNXPACE3XW7FTGUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n港版「國安法」通過後，香港人人自危，在惡法下爭取民主自由，「被送中」風險大增。專門辦理政治庇護的紐約移民律師艾飛力（Felipe Alexandre）接受《蘋果》專訪表示，「國安法」通過後，已收到逾百個來自香港、有關政治庇護的查詢，「之前反送中（形勢）雖然緊張，但還有些希望，現在真的沒有希望。」"},{"pid":"76c06295139dd5b146a2be81797b4611a42c55bf","tid":2119582,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:39:43.000Z","msg":"精通中文、在紐約皇后區執業的艾飛力坦言，過往絕少接到來自香港、有關申請政治庇護的查詢，2015年發生「銅鑼灣書店」事件後，他開始關注香港情況，「以前根本沒有（來自香港的查詢），『反送中』後接了幾宗個案。人大討論『國安法』至今，我們做了至少100個諮詢」。 他認為，「國安法」對香港人的自由造成前所未有的限制，「法律給中共太多藉口來起訴（香港人），而且判刑不可思議，我們覺得很難受。」"},{"pid":"af9a0b1b7b1ac65f88b91f5e945f0f43db9f3a2d","tid":2119582,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"對於有意到美國尋求政治庇護的港人，艾飛力指，申請政治庇護可分為兩類。第一類是申請人在自己的國家，已受到政府迫害，出於五種特殊理由之一，包括政治意見、宗教信仰、種族、國籍（如中國的新疆及西藏人）及特殊社會團體（如同性戀者）。第二類是申請人沒有在本國被逮捕或迫害，但因為入境美國後的行為，讓申請人擔心回國會被捉。"},{"pid":"84da27b8f2e18d482b2496c4436517dd32d94f07","tid":2119582,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"他以香港人為例，「不一定有參加過示威活動，有參加過當然是可以用到（申請理由）。假設你沒有參加示威，但珍惜言論自由，在美國一直發表你對『國安法』帶來影響（的意見），如教育或宗教等。如果你是這樣，便有合理理由害怕回國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。因為現在香港政府不會幫你，反而會起訴你。」"},{"pid":"7a2123ecfabb298ad1376ad19beda37eeefb4dc0","tid":2119582,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:41:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b83571ba465f587a01846b620c860bedf332e6","tid":2119582,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"住妞約更加無希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBLM+肺炎+民主左派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 美國形勢大好⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></p>"},{"pid":"35e9b9a07677327af6af026b8b717c463b6bdfb5","tid":2119582,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fd83cf95c49bc1a9440853839de1cdc5a477b18","tid":2119582,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82b83571ba465f587a01846b620c860bedf332e6","tid":2119582,"uid":70487,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"住妞約更加無希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBLM+肺炎+民主左派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 美國形勢大好⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"口裡說不"},{"pid":"8746ba28165aab84d214b2134fa70d3e490deb22","tid":2119582,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:43:07.000Z","msg"